[MUSIC PLAYING]

It starts with a gift that handles future kitchen adventures. It's Cuisinart's Elemental processor makes it fast and fun. The wide mouth feed tube preps all veggies and fruits with ease and parts are dishwasher safe. Puree homemade baby foods using the sealed tight cupwork with blade lock plus the reversible shredding and adjustable slicing disks process ingredients precisely. And when it's time to share your secret recipe, it comes together in minutes. You've always prepared family favorites. Now, it's her turn. Cuisinart's Elemental processor. Make a lifetime of cooking memories
